oen vil selvsagt si at dette er \u00e5 overdrive, men verken ledelse, personale eller elevr\u00e5d her p\u00e5 skolen oppfatter det slik. Vi vil si klart fra om at narkotika ikke aksepteres, og med en s\u00e5 synlig markering blir ogs\u00e5 hele lokalsamfunnen obs p\u00e5 problemet, sier N\u00f8ren."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "66a595ab33cc3346ac54f1d9d7ecd12e7d2052e10b2af23aef93894819341010"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-09-13T16:17:51.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "R\u00f8ros videreg\u00e5ende skole ble i dag stengt p\u00e5 grunn av rusmisbruk. Elever ruser seg i skoletida, og narkotika omsettes p\u00e5 skoleomr\u00e5det."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1033308.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20skole2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/c63c7be0896f4467afc90be1ff2f0a0d9d8609bc.jpg?593c12e6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Narkobruk stenger skole -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "c63c7be0896f4467afc90be1ff2f0a0d9d8609bc"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["videreg\u00e5ende skole", "skole", "elever"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "r\u00f8ros"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "iver n\u00f8ren"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1033308.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-defau